<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>Someone requested a reset of your password. You can do this through the link below:</p>

<p>
  <!-- Generates link like /password_resets/TOKEN/edit -->
  <%= link_to "Reset Password", edit_password_reset_url(token: @user.reset_token), style: "background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
</p>

<p>This link will expire in two hours.</p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>